description.en:
AUTH is our platform utility token. You can earn AUTH tokens by signing up, posting messages, getting
backing from your followers (backing of both your identity and your posts) and even for providing liquidity. Once you
have AUTH tokens you can back others on Authencity to participate in their rewards pools.
